Title: rse_gene_mouse_RNAseq-data
Description: RangedSummarizedExperiment of bulk RNA-seq data from mouse brain and blood at the gene level, generated by the Lieber Institute for Brain Development (LIBD) and available through the smokingMouse Bioconductor package.

Title: rse_tx_mouse_RNAseq-data
Description: RangedSummarizedExperiment of bulk RNA-seq data from mouse brain and blood at the transcript (tx) level, generated by the Lieber Institute for Brain Development (LIBD) and available through the smokingMouse Bioconductor package.

Title: rse_jx_mouse_RNAseq-data
Description: RangedSummarizedExperiment of bulk RNA-seq data from mouse brain and blood at the exon-exon junction (jx) level, generated by the Lieber Institute for Brain Development (LIBD) and available through the smokingMouse Bioconductor package.

Title: rse_exon_mouse_RNAseq-data
Description: RangedSummarizedExperiment of bulk RNA-seq data from mouse brain and blood at the exon level, generated by the Lieber Institute for Brain Development (LIBD) and available through the smokingMouse Bioconductor package.

Title: de_genes_prenatal_human_brain_smoking
Description: GRanges with the information of the differentialy expressed genes (DEG) in smoking human prenatal brain, generated by Semick SA et al. (2018), Mol Psychiatry, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41380-018-0223-1, obtained from https://github.com/LieberInstitute/Smoking_DLPFC_Devel

Title: de_genes_adult_human_brain_smoking
Description: GRanges with the information of the differentialy expressed genes (DEG) in smoking human adult brain, generated by Semick SA et al. (2018), Mol Psychiatry, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41380-018-0223-1, obtained from https://github.com/LieberInstitute/Smoking_DLPFC_Devel.
